This paper deals with resource allocation in cloud/distributed computing clusters, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also discusses fairness measures and optimization, which are topics in Game Theory (cs.GT) and Control Systems (cs.SY). The proposed mechanism involves iterative algorithms, which is a common topic in Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI).
